This has nothing to do with SRAM in $6000-$7FFF, which you correctly state is provided only by MMC1, MMC3, MMC4, MMC5, and MMC6. Arfink is talking about rewiring a cart to use SRAM instead of mask ROM or flash memory.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Sat Apr 29, 2006 6:28 am</p><hr />
