<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=1446&amp;p=12360#p12360"><![CDATA[
Battery backup needs additionnal logic that mapper 0 doesn't have. Use mapper 1 (MMC1), 4 (MMC3) or 5 (MMC5) only for battery backed games (the mapper 10, MMC4 also have battery backup possible but I doubt you'd be using that mapper).<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Sat Apr 29, 2006 12:38 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
